    # Calculate the mean of x and y vectors

    y_mean = np.mean(y)
    
    # Calculate the sums
    SS_tot = np.sum((y - y_mean)**2)
    SS_res = np.sum((y - x)**2)
    
    # Calculate R2
    r2 = 1 - (SS_res / SS_tot)
    
    return r2
